This is a Turn Based Battle game. In this project, i used stack. Soldiers were stored in the stack.

Game Explanation:
•Add soldiers to a specific side with their health and strength values.
•Add random soldiers to a specific side with random health and strength values.
•Initiate a fight between soldiers from two sides.
•Remove a soldier from a specific side.
•End the game when both sides have no soldiers left.

A command -> Add soldier
F command -> Fight between soldiers
R command -> Create soldier with random strength and health
C command -> Kill soldier



